---
title: Indian Inspired Fish Pie with Mustard Seed Mash, Roasted Garlic Tenderstem® and Tomatoes
description: A comfort food classic using premium ingredients, this Indian Inspired Fish Pie brings the best of the British pub into your kitchen.

Say hello to a fresh ingredient - fish pie mix! Delicious in fish pies but also all kinds of seafood dishes, this versatile mix contains flavoursome haddock, delicate cod and flaky salmon.

